{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"063b8396c7","title":"周恩来对外交部谈陈毅问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2f0a083725","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":16,"articleId":"063b8396c7","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"陈毅","id":"1feb996ca7","type":"人物"},{"name":"王力","id":"20ebde32a6","type":"人物"},{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3be77c83a5","type":"title","text":"周恩来对外交部谈陈毅问题","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fcacb3b15","type":"paragraph","text":"〖9月16日，周总理在人民大会堂接见外宾后，对外交部刘祥伦等同志作了谈话。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"56bba3997f","type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅是有严重错误，亚非会议上有严重错误，对阿尔及利亚问题有严重错误，他认为是革命的，我说是政变，他还说是革命的。他随刘少奇出访，刘少奇是典型的三降一灭，他也会有错误。一月份让他过了关，以后他又发那么大脾气，无怪小将抓住他不放，这个情绪是可以理解的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"106a9abc18","type":"paragraph","text":"但是毛主席说：“陈毅同志还是要一批二保。”","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a1ae8e9da","type":"paragraph","text":"外交部和另外的部就是不一样，陈毅这个部长和别的部长就是不一样，这是关系到国家威信和威望的问题，不是保他个人，不是保他的面子。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f372b215d6","type":"paragraph","text":"（当有人谈到联络站二十五个战斗队、组开会批判王力问题时）总理说：王力问题不要开会批判了，联络站有问题可以关门整风，外交部要自己搞运动，不要受外界影响。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"768fd71d3c","type":"paragraph","text":"又14日晚，总理接见柬埔寨外宾之余与翻译班同学谈了几个问题，大意如下：","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c163839bd0","type":"paragraph","text":"1、陈毅的大字报、大标语等不能上街；","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87f1740043","type":"paragraph","text":"2、对陈毅的态度是“一批二保”，这是最高指示；","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05c01ca770","type":"paragraph","text":"3、王力的问题要相信中央能解决，你们不要贴大字报、大标语，中央不会象有些大字报那样无限上纲。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"063b8396c7","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}